reports.job_description: We are hiring a Senior Accountant to own the monthly close and deliver accurate financial statements. Responsibilities include general ledger accounting, journal entries, accruals and prepaids, balance sheet reconciliations, AP/AR review, fixed assets and depreciation, variance analysis, and supporting external audit. Requirements: 3+ years accounting experience, strong Excel (pivot tables, VLOOKUP/XLOOKUP), knowledge of GAAP/IFRS, experience with ERP systems (SAP/Oracle/NetSuite) and/or QuickBooks, and strong attention to detail.

We are hiring a Finance Analyst to support budgeting, forecasting, and monthly reporting. Responsibilities include financial modeling, variance analysis, KPI dashboards, and supporting leadership with actionable insights. You will work closely with accounting to ensure data integrity and compliance. Requirements: 3+ years in finance or FP&A, strong Excel (pivot tables, VLOOKUP/XLOOKUP), knowledge of accounting basics (GAAP/IFRS), experience with ERP systems (SAP/Oracle/NetSuite) and/or QuickBooks, and attention to detail.

We are hiring an HR Generalist to support recruiting, onboarding, employee relations, and HR operations. Responsibilities include coordinating interviews, maintaining employee records, supporting payroll/benefits processes, ensuring compliance with company policies, and assisting with performance management. Requirements: strong communication skills, experience with HRIS (e.g., Workday, BambooHR), knowledge of employment law basics, confidentiality, and 2+ years in HR or related roles.

We are hiring a Sales Executive to manage the full sales pipeline from lead generation to closing. Responsibilities include prospecting, product demos, negotiation, maintaining CRM, achieving monthly targets, and reporting pipeline health. Requirements: 2+ years in B2B sales, strong communication and relationship-building skills, experience with CRM tools (e.g., Salesforce, HubSpot), and a track record of meeting or exceeding quotas.
